message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as the paper deals with similarity measures for sound retrieval. Other likely categories include cs.SD, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, and cs.MM. cs.SD deals with sound and music processing, which is the main focus of this paper. cs.CL deals with natural language processing, which is related to the vocalisation aspect of the paper. cs.LG and cs.AI deal with machine learning and deep learning, which are the methods used in this paper. cs.MM deals with multimedia processing, which is also relevant to this paper as it deals with audio and visual data.
